x-sap-shortText: API to access compensation information for an employee.

x-servers.description: OData APIs for the SuccessFactors Data Centers

info.title: Compensation Information
info.description: API to access compensation information for an employee such as salary, recurring bonuses and non recurring compensation information. It is also used to create non-recurring deductions in a payment.
